c: 9
v: 112
t: "(Abasezeranyijwe ijuru ni) abicuza, abagaragira (Allah), abashimira (Allah), abasiba, abunama (basenga), abubama (basenga), ababwiriza gukora ibyiza, ababuza gukora ibibi n'abitondera amategeko ya Allah (bakurikiza amategeko ye). Unahe inkuru nziza abemeramana (yo kuzagororerwa ijuru)"